---
title: Speedy Thai Inspired Beef Noodles with Stir-Fried Pepper and Carrot Ribbons
description: On the table in less than 25 minutes, these Speedy Thai Inspired Beef Noodles have it all. Thai spices, ketjap manis and honey turn beef mince into a tasty topping for egg noodles.
